
<h3 style='color:red;'>{{ "Thank you for using the DARIAH ELDAH Consent Form Wizard. You can obtain the text for your consent form by downloading it from this page. Please note that you will be provided raw text only. Please also be aware that for data privacy reasons, the information you entered in the tool to obtain your consent form will not be stored and will be lost when closing the website. If you want to provide your result as an example for other CFW users, please send it to us at <a href='mailto:eldah@dariah.eu'>eldah@dariah.eu</a>"|trans }}
</h3>
<br/>
<h2><a href='#' id='get-raw-text' >{{ "Download the Raw text"|trans }}</a></h2>
<br/>
<div class='scenario-full-text'>
    <h1> {{ "Information on Data Processing and Declaration of Consent"|trans }} </h1>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="py-5 text-center">
          <h2>{{ "Introduction"|trans }}</h2>
            <p class="lead">
